A State Of Trance Radio Top 20 - August 2013 Including Classic Bonus Track (2013) 

                                Trance | Armada Music 

              320 kbps | MP3 | Unmixed | 2013-08-09 | 02:08:40 | 304 Mb



After the grand success of Armin van Buuren's 'Intense' album, the world's number one DJ brings his most popular monthly package, the A State of Trance Radio Top 20. The Top 20 include his personal favourites, as well as the favourites of the more than 25 million listeners of his weekly radio show A State of Trance. The August 2013 pack includes the tunes of Airbase, Ferry Corsten, Orjan Nilsen, Daniel Kandi, Super 8 & Tab, Cosmic Gate, Alexandre Bergheau, Sean Tyas and more.
